{"tid":454322,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解可以中意一個人但又唔愛佢","createTime":"2017-11-01T04:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T04:09:05.000Z","uid":28333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2ecaeec94a25e9d174f289d0ee40710d239ccdbc","tid":454322,"uid":28333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:29:09.000Z","msg":"如題"},{"pid":"95e4b365666e5883c6e0f4dd2a3b40fac3c6622c","tid":454322,"uid":22243,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:37:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如題</blockquote><br />\n因為個心有另一個愛既人收埋左"},{"pid":"f3e82f45db68100c0aa94403b679d8d45bb9f4e0","tid":454322,"uid":28333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T11:08:45.000Z","msg":"咁點解又要同個男既一齊呢"},{"pid":"a665cc0ab91b3c63ef2667957c9094da77640e83","tid":454322,"uid":60936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T11:50:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0d1c48fa022e252096f9d601a7ac2c20c2b82b","tid":454322,"uid":12360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T11:52:32.000Z","msg":"藉口黎嫁姐"},{"pid":"39accbfb5e04dbf1b371374df7b102508b93f248","tid":454322,"uid":92456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T12:51:45.000Z","msg":"鐘意同愛係唔同程度嚟喎清"},{"pid":"a0dd7e6abe6178b8361f1c5b06799b58f75c2a6a","tid":454322,"uid":153232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T19:09:44.000Z","msg":"點解可以愛一個人但唔中意佢"},{"pid":"d498a2fca25a0e0621bee322d87de66ce60b27f9","tid":454322,"uid":153232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T19:10:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鐘意同愛係唔同程度嚟喎清</blockquote><br />\n講多小小可以嗎？我想了解更多"},{"pid":"4117cf41a7afb2b2978b71e8c71f37a32780cdb0","tid":454322,"uid":117752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T19:20:23.000Z","msg":"心入面收埋一個人，無論遇到幾好既人，都比唔上一個佢"},{"pid":"e46ba6fc2a412ab5f554253773c14be05965c99b","tid":454322,"uid":92456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T23:24:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鐘意同愛係唔同程度嚟喎清</blockquote><br />\n講多小小可以嗎？我想了解更多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人認為鐘意係一種好強烈嘅好感(就算認識唔深)<br />\n但愛係要同對方經歷過好多嘢之後日子耐咗慢慢產生嘅"},{"pid":"25d8826c107dd37ac68cb342a14e90ca85847e70","tid":454322,"uid":28333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T02:48:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>心入面收埋一個人，無論遇到幾好既人，都比唔上一個佢</blockquote><br />\n跟整就係咁，但唔明點解要同我一齊"},{"pid":"523fc52251fc5f7c7f368205acff85c756d7eed3","tid":454322,"uid":28333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T02:49:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>心入面收埋一個人，無論遇到幾好既人，都比唔上一個佢</blockquote><br />\n跟整就係咁，但唔明點解要同我一齊</blockquote><br />\n跟本"},{"pid":"3a86db3eea3edf230d0e54e58f1a0f8b1b798e65","tid":454322,"uid":132361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T02:57:00.000Z","msg":"鍾意係種情感黎 好易發生<br />\n鍾意係會令你好似突然食咗禁藥咁 突然變咗個人都得 可能係人生最大作用嘅激素<br />\n<br />\n但係愛係一種選擇 一種承諾<br />\n你愛一個人 代表你想同佢生活落去 代表你願意令佢成為自己生命中嘅一部分<br />\n係一種比較偏向負責任嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n我鍾意你 但係我唔愛你<br />\n其實就有d 我鍾意屌你 但係我唔想同你生仔一樣嘅意思<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所有咁講嘅人都係仆街黎</span></span><br />\n走吧啦施主 你唔係以為同佢一齊就會幸福啊嘛<br />\n我話你知 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冇</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">因為我試過。</span>"},{"pid":"79cbc94c41054e819373c67a85f7bd30ce7dc439","tid":454322,"uid":22243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:07:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鐘意同愛係唔同程度嚟喎清</blockquote><br />\n講多小小可以嗎？我想了解更多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人認為鐘意係一種好強烈嘅好感(就算認識唔深)<br />\n但愛係要同對方經歷過好多嘢之後日子耐咗慢慢產生嘅</blockquote><br />\n正確 愛係要歷練 識左人一兩個月就話好撚愛 咪玩啦"},{"pid":"114a3974359fa20e191f79dc100a84f346638a6a","tid":454322,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:09:05.000Z","msg":"like同love係兩回事"}]}